<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>API Expiry Notice</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f6fa;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #1a1a2e;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px;
    }
    .info-block {
      background: #f1f1f1;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-top: 15px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>API Expiry Warning</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello Admin,</p>

      <p>This is to notify you that one of your active API subscriptions is <strong>about to expire</strong>.</p>

      <div class="info-block">
        <p><strong>API Name:</strong> <%= api.name %></p>
        <p><strong>Plan:</strong> <%= api.premium_plan.plan %></p>
        <p><strong>Billing Cycle:</strong> <%= api.premium_plan.billing_cycle %></p>
        <p><strong>Price:</strong> $<%= api.premium_plan.price_usd %></p>
        <p><strong>Start Date:</strong> <%= api.start_on %></p>
        <p><strong>Expires On:</strong> <%= api.expires_on %></p>
        <p><strong>Days Remaining:</strong> <%= api.days_remaining %></p>
        <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span style="color:#d85600;">Expiring Soon</span></p>
      </div>

      <p>Please take action to renew the subscription to avoid service interruption.</p>

      <p>Regards,<br />
      <strong><%= site_name %></strong> System</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= site_name %>. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
